{"tid":654761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度政府落柯打 要求民眾唔好用手拎飯食？！","createTime":"2018-05-06T02:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T12:03:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c87924024090c8c58287805717b7972d6d89da","tid":654761,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"講起印度人嘅飲食習慣，大家必定諗起就係傳統嘅直接用手拎飯食，唔少旅客去到印度都會叫自己試一試，不過我諗大家都唔係好習慣用手直接接觸食物。不過近日印度政府就落咗柯打，大力宣傳叫大家唔好接觸完紙幣之後再用手食飯；印度食品安全及標準局就話唔少食客都直接用手接觸紙幣再食飯，另一方面餐廳老闆多數兼做廚師同收銀，變相將紙幣上嘅微生物同細菌不斷傳播。有數字顯示，印度食物中毒個案數字不斷上升，尤其引發社區唔少老人、小朋友嘅腸胃疾病。當局目前希望宣傳大家要將紙幣分開處理，並且話會導致泌尿系統、敗血症、皮膚感染、中毒性休克、腦膜炎等。據知下一步政府將會硬性規定食店、學校、醫院都要分開處理收銀及煮食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vGEpyAOnAzzlre6fyFqTCA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/10693d7470a7e2f5fb9a99eeeabb29db\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvGEpyAOnAzzlre6fyFqTCA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F10693d7470a7e2f5fb9a99eeeabb29db&h=b1590e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度人用手食飯係千年傳統，歷久不衰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9WdWRp71tj2P7o6.eVV4EQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY1O2g9NDE3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/332ce1b6c926b23f69030f5f9cea7bab\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9WdWRp71tj2P7o6.eVV4EQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY1O2g9NDE3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F332ce1b6c926b23f69030f5f9cea7bab&h=5a5913f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府開始要求大家唔好一邊接觸食物一邊用錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VxgCMU9yhes64I6IHq3Gow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIxO2g9NDE0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/5549fb572b12efa55d38bb81adb653d3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVxgCMU9yhes64I6IHq3Gow--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIxO2g9NDE0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F5549fb572b12efa55d38bb81adb653d3&h=9dcafcca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔少餐廳員工都係收銀煮食一腳踢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hktravelnow.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%90%BD%E6%9F%AF%E6%89%93-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%8B%8E%E9%A3%AF%E9%A3%9F-150856865.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhktravelnow.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%259F%25AF%25E6%2589%2593-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258B%258E%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E9%25A3%259F-150856865.html&d=65zmiEDbFJOKx0AN6DD1dL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=630da67a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hktravelnow.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%90%BD%E6%9F%AF%E6%89%93-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E6%8B%8E%E9%A3%AF%E9%A3%9F-150856865.html</a>"},{"pid":"01eaa2f1c1a75565285859b1da612aa9824e1c81","tid":654761,"uid":1654,"like":214,"dislike":1,"score":213,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:14:51.000Z","msg":"強姦國終於有新聞唔關強姦事"},{"pid":"b60d0fbb56ee479528aa67e487c59d9418ccb7f2","tid":654761,"uid":42188,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/160838_d712607da98b26ec9034ffedefaef7cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F160838_d712607da98b26ec9034ffedefaef7cf.jpg&h=73a2b800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/160838_b2e453fd6398e95df588a26111f06885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l